" />"},{"pid":"e9c2d1876a678b4e8037c65af58b65d2ab86922e","tid":472176,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連戒j既意志力都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e35e6897b7375ad4570466e19bb6da5683dc4d","tid":472176,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb28681edf1a719333951b5db40a32040b506f33","tid":472176,"uid":118314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"搵個人同你一齊做<br />\n認真"},{"pid":"2eb9dd159169242c9d2340cdd17065312e265705","tid":472176,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"首先要知你點解要做果樣野，會唔會係信念唔夠強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：做乜都持續唔到超過2日"},{"pid":"c10b5c2a986b9954cdf0b4528befcf57d1201125","tid":472176,"uid":79686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T00:54:45.000Z","msg":"要提升意志力要訓練 堅持練要意志力.......<br />\n<br />\n坐係到個腦loop下就提升到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e778ecda61e62425ea2934cdf480fcaae3ad2e93","tid":472176,"uid":84924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T07:13:02.000Z","msg":"一個幾出名嘅方法係將一個好大嘅目標拆做一個個細嘅目標<br />\neg <br />\n練好啲英文<br />\n-&gt; 唔用字幕睇一套戲<br />\n對鐘講英文兩分鐘<br />\n寫一百字隨筆<br />\n<br />\n將啲大嘢拆做細嘢<br />\n將啲虛嘢變做實嘢<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法唔係提升你意志力<br />\n而係將task嘅難度 變到你意志力可以承受嘅水平"},{"pid":"0e87f518075d0d550df6ec1e2d7ce0350b996a6f","tid":472176,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"最緊要係耐力，例如你定左每一做一個小目標就唔可以俾任何藉口自己有一日skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e32172bb9a77f4af8aa4c9209faaf232715f3d","tid":472176,"uid":70219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:01:18.000Z","msg":"首次定較容易達到的目標,完成後有成功感,先可以加強你達成較後目標既心<br />\n以學好英文為例, 每日學3個英文生字, 先試連續3日, OK 再加變5日/7日/2星期/1個月咁.<br />\n<br />\n不過, 問心其實講到尾睇你有幾想去做, 每人都好多目標想去做, 但都好快會放棄. 實情係你自己都無「動機」去做, 你有「動機」就乜都有心有耐性去做架啦.<br />\n調番轉講 「放棄」都係自己的選擇, 即係代表你自己都唔想時間落去<br />\n問清楚自己想點先再去做啦, 唔係只會覺得自己越黎越無用"},{"pid":"1d51934d7fdc6e0ee885babb86ebba6f3f18efdb","tid":472176,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c760d0340713d2dae05664744d7c3d89061a2f7a","tid":472176,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"自言自語"},{"pid":"f189745f09f27f164c9bf0471048a30c46bd0e9a","tid":472176,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b88Hj_P1SKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb88Hj_P1SKE&d=fBvdNhVp%2B76asYHKo078YFKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=65faf2cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b88Hj_P1SKE</a>"},{"pid":"ae192532fac4ffe6631bc670d0135b39b3ac9b6d","tid":472176,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7410e07f75179d3f93bb05dd76a237cd2ed08af5","tid":472176,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"你有冇女"},{"pid":"dbb3f0f85afbeed25d79d97eb3701b1a582d1fb7","tid":472176,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:39:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e458d546f29600703ebbfedfeceaad07f5de196","tid":472176,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T17:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00afd23d9e6110eaa88b500f72abc2677fd63c3c","tid":472176,"uid":70760,"lik